_:N9df598964f364ae69d5ef0447dd21406 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Charlie is Group Chief Financial Officer and Board member of International Workplace Group Plc, the world’s largest office provider with its Regus and Spaces brands across 120 countries, employing 10,000+ people and a member of the UK’s FTSE 250 index. He is also a Non-Executive Board Member of AICPA-CIMA, the largest accounting body globally. </p>\n\n<p>Prior to this, he was Chief Financial Officer of Babylon, a US-based digital-first, value-based healthcare provider, holding this position from November 2017 to October 2022. Charlie has also served in various roles, including as Global Head of Corporate Development at CMC Markets, a retail-focused financial services business (September 2014 to November 2017), Vice President at Deutsche Bank (October 2008 to August 2014), and has also worked at Lehman Brothers and IBM. </p>\n\n<p>Charlie holds a MA in Economics and Management from the University of Oxford.</p>\n" .
_:N9df598964f364ae69d5ef0447dd21406 <http://schema.org/name> "Charlie Steel" .
